                                              Angular -Front end technology

                                                    Basic commands 
                                              -----------------------------
                                       1.creation of angular-ng new project name

                                       2.To run angular project-ng serve --open

                                       3.component creation - ng g c component-name

                                       4.Service creation - ng g s service-name

                                       


                                                   Basic Concepts
                                               ---------------------  
                                       1.Module -To import third party library -root Module -AppModule

                                       2.Components -html,css,ts

                                       3.To set up path for component - App routing module file

                                       4.routing-outlet selector

                                       5.Angular services  

                                       6.Dependency injention -inside contructor
                                          syntax:access specifier object-name:dependent-class-name 

                                       7.asynchronous - rxjs - Observable-subscribe()  

                                       8.Data binding - sharing data inside a component
                                           8.1  One way binding
                                                 8.1.1 component to view
                                                        1.String interpolation - {{variable-name}}
                                                        2.Property binding - [attribute] = "property-name"

                                                 8.1.2 view to component
                                                   8.1.2.1 Event Binding - (event) = "function call"
                                                   8.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event - (event) = "function-call($event)"
                                                   8.1.2.3 Templete reference variable, #variable-name

                                           8.2  Two way binding
                                                8.2.1  ngModel (Templete driven angular forms) 
                                                  -Import FormsModule , [(ngModel)] ="variable name"
                                                  -ngSubmit - apply it in form tag , (ngSubmit) ="function call"


                                       9.Angular directives - To dominate DOM
                                          9.1 Component Directive
                                          9.2 Structural Directive -  to add/remove html elements
                                              1. *ngIf ="condition"
                                              2. *ngFor = "let variable-name of array-name"

                                      10.ActivatedRoute - Provides access to information about a route associated with
                                      
                                      11.Router class - use navigateByUrl() to navigate one to another using ts

                                      12.Pipe - to convert user input to another format


                                        

                                                
                                                        